{"tid":2388370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰提醒旅客：可用永久性居民身份證離開香港","createTime":"2021-01-31T05:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T08:14:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36d0d85912852c894a39e057c0b7fcfe5194f3e1","tid":2388370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573267-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573267-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=c8893594\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573267-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3f0d11b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573267-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空在網站公布，因應特區政府宣布由今日起，英國國民（海外）護照BNO 不再被視為有效旅行證件或身份證明，國泰提醒旅客注意BNO不能用於在香港出入境，香港居民可繼續以特區護照或<strong><span class=\"red\">香港永久性居民身份證</span></strong>入境或<strong><span class=\"red\">離開香港</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空又表示，乘客登機前往香港的航班時，航空公司會要求相關香港居民出示特區護照或香港永久性居民身份證，以作證明。至於未持有其他有效旅行證件的非中國籍香港永久性居民，可向入境處申領簽證身分書，以作國際旅行之用。"},{"pid":"6469dd8d1c7e53a8dd95b393f866a1f504193d24","tid":2388370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3846ff227165c61d85541d769fee65ec7257efa","tid":2388370,"uid":331739,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"航空公司只需要確保你可以入境目的地 同成功出境就得"},{"pid":"088a56dda201b715c03dbdc07602ebeede9586dc","tid":2388370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5668858be9b8f49d2466f48b2ed4b35ebfaa75","tid":2388370,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3846ff227165c61d85541d769fee65ec7257efa","tid":2388370,"uid":331739,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"航空公司只需要確保你可以入境目的地 同成功出境就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"Fat finger唔小心小負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef0a23236fb63cb20588e0e1b63de5abaabfd23","tid":2388370,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"人之將死 其言也善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8abcd047333b48cd0abb5efa20c787834e65782","tid":2388370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5bc5d3df79b3d499555feb6624f66a7c0cec0b","tid":2388370,"uid":128594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"唔係一向可以用身份證離境？"},{"pid":"54a3a72527ad0c468cce7f22b7c82f8d0c6afe70","tid":2388370,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5bc5d3df79b3d499555feb6624f66a7c0cec0b","tid":2388370,"uid":128594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"唔係一向可以用身份證離境？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n所以提醒下你地"},{"pid":"02b75333ca11be30ef097bf9f344e3d0bd20669a","tid":2388370,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲係<br />\n不過佢講到BNO5＋1之後取消埋你身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm